{"tid":294643,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救!!!]狗仔一個月嘔幾次","createTime":"2017-06-23T06:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T14:37:26.000Z","uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1edc49f33608c1f61c11383270af665306b07eb","tid":294643,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻五個月大既銀狐仔呢一個月嘔左4-5次 唔係連續<br />\n但每次我都係返緊工我女朋友打比我話我知, 佢話係啡啡地色無血<br />\n佢話個衰仔嘔完之後無特別好動/低落<br />\n但我每返到屋企見佢成晚都好似平時咁活潑 睇落完全無問題 而我女朋友就好緊張...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢通常都係出完街既第二日朝早嘔 <br />\nGoogle左之後 大部份既網站都話咁其實無大問題<br />\n<br />\n但我地都唔係好放心 有無巴打可以解答到小弟佢發生咩事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁係正常定唔正常?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f755b2e6d7771a9b9c4eda85df2d5ae2e93f7cda","tid":294643,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"以前隻北京狗都試過嘔黃色水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住佢"},{"pid":"07aac85d49c46a921a87dffb182f586611c29167","tid":294643,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},{"pid":"907579be46f02b91cebad1f067f16ed54db04b70","tid":294643,"uid":68919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"有冇經常掃地 食返自己d毛/地下d污穢野都會嘔"},{"pid":"ed8489242627098f3d149e11f6057864cdd55bea","tid":294643,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前隻北京狗都試過嘔黃色水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eb376272a281cfb8c2a8159381314ba47805db","tid":294643,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"會唔會食咗毛<br />\n試下比嘔毛膏佢食<br />\n<br />\n每日分三餐<br />\n如果乾糧加微暖水比佢食<br />\n或用攪拌機打碎啲糧"},{"pid":"a94ac02934fa801e1b906b7c4f7553f228d76c40","tid":294643,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇經常掃地 食返自己d毛/地下d污穢野都會嘔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩,三日吸一次塵 屋企都叫唔污穢"},{"pid":"a443636a158993e1b2859fb3020232129d733f74","tid":294643,"uid":68919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇經常掃地 食返自己d毛/地下d污穢野都會嘔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩,三日吸一次塵 屋企都叫唔污穢</blockquote><br />\n日日都吸會好d 屋企得一隻狗？仲有冇其他動物"},{"pid":"2b7c19a7983025be33a4316f5999f8dd48c7eb27","tid":294643,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會食咗毛<br />\n試下比嘔毛膏佢食<br />\n<br />\n每日分三餐<br />\n如果乾糧加微暖水比佢食<br />\n或用攪拌機打碎啲糧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食毛都會嘔? 但佢唔係立即嘔 嘔親都係朝早10點,11點嘔<br />\n我平時沈淋哂啲糧先比佢食"},{"pid":"6325a428ae1c8f36c2576dbf5a073e46d1a7ca59","tid":294643,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇經常掃地 食返自己d毛/地下d污穢野都會嘔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩,三日吸一次塵 屋企都叫唔污穢</blockquote><br />\n日日都吸會好d 屋企得一隻狗？仲有冇其他動物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無啦 得佢一隻咋...."},{"pid":"38c88880442262f1a0267c92805c81fdea1c399e","tid":294643,"uid":68919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re